<li id="cite_note-territory-19"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-territory_19-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">* <cite id="CITEREFBenedikter2006" class="citation web cs1">Benedikter, Thomas (2006-06-19). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080309063149/http://www.gfbv.it/3dossier/eu-min/autonomy.html">"The working autonomies in Europe"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Society_for_Threatened_Peoples" title="Society for Threatened Peoples">Society for Threatened Peoples</a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.gfbv.it/3dossier/eu-min/autonomy.html">the original</a> on 2008-03-09<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2019-08-30</span></span>. <q>Denmark has established very specific territorial autonomies with its two island territories</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+working+autonomies+in+Europe&amp;rft.pub=Society+for+Threatened+Peoples&amp;rft.date=2006-06-19&amp;rft.aulast=Benedikter&amp;rft.aufirst=Thomas&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gfbv.it%2F3dossier%2Feu-min%2Fautonomy.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFlag+of+Denmark" class="Z3988"></span>
<ul><li><cite id="CITEREFAckrén2017" class="citation web cs1">Ackrén, Maria (November 2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20190830110832/http://www.world-autonomies.info/tas/Greenland/Pages/default.aspx">"Greenland"</a>. Autonomy Arrangements in the World. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.world-autonomies.info/tas/Greenland/Pages/default.aspx">the original</a> on 2019-08-30<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2019-08-30</span></span>. <q>Faroese and Greenlandic are seen as official regional languages in the self-governing territories belonging to Denmark.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Greenland&amp;rft.pub=Autonomy+Arrangements+in+the+World&amp;rft.date=2017-11&amp;rft.aulast=Ackr%C3%A9n&amp;rft.aufirst=Maria&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.world-autonomies.info%2Ftas%2FGreenland%2FPages%2Fdefault.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFlag+of+Denmark" class="Z3988"></span></li>
